src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n党台我只欣賞視點31，可摷我帖，佢一開節目我已經讚呢班明顯係後生比同台個班愛支Hea老有Heart有料得多！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"175135e4dbde88918c8d17d7371e1935b3cfd4d2","tid":1886860,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0496521b6f52414cacb0e4e719c4cde294f5a7","tid":1886860,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:18:22.000Z","msg":"轉載 － 為正面回應曾志豪呼籲，請大家寫email去廣播處長支持 #頭條新聞<br />\n<br />\n毅進仔已經動員數百人投訴香港電台，請用email支持頭條新聞，最好的結果就是令到投訴 變成小數支持成為大多數，可以保護頭條新聞和香港電台，即或不然，政府有了支持的信件，將來也可 回顧今天，給不公平對待的人，還他們清白。<br />\n<br />\n轉載 － 為正面回應曾志豪呼籲，請大家寫email去廣播處長支持《頭條新聞》。可用以下template:<br />\n<br />\nTo: kwleung@rthk.hk<br />\nCc: ccu@rthk.hk<br />\n-------------------<br />\nDear Director of Broadcasting,<br />\n<br />\nI'm writing to indicate my full support for RTHK, in particular its programme《頭條新聞》, for its unbiased reporting and commenting of current events. Recently, an episode of this programme had touched on the questionable allocation of medical resources to the HK Police and their work (or lack thereof) in fighting against the coronavirus. I believe the majority of the people of HK who truly care about the society and follow closely the development of current events would agree with what the programme had reported and commented in this recent episode. Hence, I think the letter from the PPRB of HK Police, which criticizes the programme for its recent reporting, is inappropriate and constitutes a blatant intervention of the freedom of press.<br />\n<br />\nPlease continue your hardwork for the benefit of the society.<br />\n<br />\nRegards<br />\n［打自己名］"},{"pid":"2b6bcea40f02e84e36b075624751df19084b020a","tid":1886860,"uid":71373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00aa9e4eb48baae06325812dc7ad03e74a00bde5","tid":1886860,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f9b32a2662dfe68d9d7f7ccd87989771e7f3ab","tid":1886860,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270603a90fc12fcd6398294c3f786ca042612254","tid":1886860,"uid":34725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d72d11e96982b5b3fcce04789e45dd89ca79f06","tid":1886860,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90c784559db73919c14b461a078dcffe6768562b","tid":1886860,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://chng.it/fDDPDpG7GB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FfDDPDpG7GB&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=37e6790b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/fDDPDpG7GB</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有聯署要推！<br />\n<br />\n【港台節目顧問團13成員促梁家榮尊重頭條新聞言論自由】<br />\n<br />\n13名香港電台節目顧問團成員向廣播處長梁家榮發表公開信，指《頭條新聞》最新一集播出後被警察及多方追擊，顧問要求梁家榮秉持香港言論自由、開放多元的核心價值，包容、尊重和支持《頭條新聞》創作人員的編輯決定。公開信邀請市民聯署，截至下午3時，有逾萬人聯署。<br />\n<br />\n參與聯署包括大律師公會執委石書銘、香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑、資訊科技界立法會議員莫乃光、融樂會創辦人王惠芬、嶺大文化研究系副教授梁旭明、學者張楚勇等。<br />\n<br />\n他們指出，《頭條新聞》自1989年起一直用「嬉笑怒罵」諷刺幽默表達手法針貶時弊，透過諷刺戲劇鋪陳社會情緒，加深市民對時事認識，對促進議論公共事務和監察政府施政起着重要作用。<br />\n<br />\n公開信表示，警方日前去信梁家榮就時事諷刺節目《頭條新聞》涉及警隊的内容作嚴重指控，屬於干預港台運作，顧問憂慮港台的節目創作自由會被打壓，或者因政府要求《頭條新聞》製作團隊自我審查，損害創作、言論和表達自由，形成寒蟬效應，因此發信支持《頭條新聞》繼續為市民發聲。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #頭條新聞 #梁家榮 #言論自由 #石書銘 #方保僑 #莫乃光"},{"pid":"03101dbf3712a73c2bf049749cecc84011004acb","tid":1886860,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e588c3365e3c85a56ef542ffe6bd3abc3af4b96","tid":1886860,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71338e233f3cfcc95b21140beabfab21ed80da1","tid":1886860,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:20:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbd5a37695e9e956f27f3d4848a64c167ee0e563","tid":1886860,"uid":335058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699bce2199b014a20d84a08e21c7ab95eed831fc","tid":1886860,"uid":179936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:00:36.000Z","msg":"呢個好似無人推咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89458b51e0f633266e76718f50b9e2792d5b780d